source.name: Broome County Annual Employee Earnings: Beginning 2009
source.description:
The County of Broome Personnel Department produces a
report annually containing the Name, Title, Department,
Base Earnings and Over Time Earnings of each employee
who has held a position within the County anytime during
that year.
